dark colors more than pale ones.

516
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:11,664
Help me choose.

517
00:32:12,300 --> 00:32:13,424
Which one should I wear?

518
00:32:13,456 --> 00:32:14,664
Dark or light?

519
00:32:14,696 --> 00:32:16,144
Just wear whichever.

520
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,208
How about this one?

521
00:32:17,248 --> 00:32:18,400
