523
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,888
Won’t it be too extra though?

524
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,752
I’m just going to walk past his room.

525
00:32:24,776 --> 00:32:25,664
What did you say?

526
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:26,960
I’m going to walk past his room.

527
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:29,000
Gosh, I don’t know anymore.

528
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:31,264
Help me!

529
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:34,576
Just pick whichever color you want.

530
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:35,424
It’s your choice.

531
00:32:35,456 --> 00:32:36,832
Why are you irritated?

532
00:32:39,140 --> 00:32:41,384
If I were an overthinker,

533
00:32:41,416 --> 00:32:43,860
I’d think you’re jealous.

534
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,472
You’re quite delusional.

535
00:32:52,624 --> 00:32:54,620
Paul likes navy blue.

536
00:32:54,990 --> 00:32:57,456
I saw him using a navy blue phone case.

537
00:32:57,504 --> 00:32:58,504
Really?

538
00:32:59,140 --> 00:32:59,808
Yeah.

539
00:32:59,848 --> 00:33:00,848
Thanks.

540
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:37,880
It’s trending?

541
00:33:39,408 --> 00:33:41,320
Wait, what’s with the spike
in engagement?

542
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,400
Forgiving someone isn’t a big deal,

543
00:33:48,424 --> 00:33:50,400
but giving them a chance is hard.

544
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:54,296
Phi’s trying to ask for a second chance
with a guilty heart.

545
00:33:54,328 --> 00:33:56,072
If you’ve forgiven him,

546
00:33:56,120 --> 00:33:58,070
don’t forget to give him that chance too.

547
00:33:58,104 --> 00:34:00,808
Let’s give someone
a chance to move forward.

548
00:34:00,840 --> 00:34:05,608
PrincePadtaphi SupportPhi

549
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:15,232
(THANK YOU:)

550
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:54,860
Oh.

551
00:34:55,820 --> 00:34:57,224
There’s still a lot to do.

552
00:36:54,850 --> 00:36:55,448
Hey.

553
00:36:55,472 --> 00:36:57,016
- Shh!
- Morning, Gaogie.

554
00:36:59,128 --> 00:37:00,128
Oh.

555
00:37:03,730 --> 00:37:05,256
How was your date?

556
00:37:07,530 --> 00:37:08,632
It was good.

557
00:37:08,850 --> 00:37:09,560
She looks just like her pictures.

558
00:37:09,592 --> 00:37:10,816
She’s cute.

559
00:37:11,020 --> 00:37:15,192
